I was scared to smoke it lol, but it did the trick and I went from puking and dry heaving, to eating everyt...‚Äù

It's good stuff and let me feeling happy and worrying less about shit that didn't matter. I smoked this bud and kicked it at a party with the dude my ex cheated on me with. We even smoked the cheese together. We just chilled out and had a good time. I'm also French, I know good cheese.‚Äù
